channel.title: Refined Power: no documentation of Micro Reactor
channel.description:
The Arc Reactor is documented, but not the Micro Reactor, though it's Tier is listed.
I'm just going to keep pumping Advanced Reactor Cores in and see if it produces power at some percentage...
